Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation out of all activity executions in the event log
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all cases

Name: Frequency of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation occurrences across all cases
Metric: Number of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities

Name: Percentage of variants that include First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation following SW-EIC Accept
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'SW-EIC Accept'

Name: Number of times First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation is immediately preceded by First Look-Your updates are overdue
Metric: Number of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities for cases where activity 'First Look-Your updates are overdue' occurs

Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation activities that occur after a revision cycle (i.e., after RW-EIC Accept or RW-EIC Minor Revision)
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'RW-EIC Accept'

Name: Ratio of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation to Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Percentage of variants where First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation appears before Awaiting Assignment to Batch
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Awaiting Assignment to Batch'

Name: Frequency of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation in cases that ultimately lead to Manuscript Export Succeeded after revision
Metric: Number of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities for cases where activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' occurs

Name: Percentage of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation that are part of the longest process variant (performance > 37,000,000)
Metric: the average of the function base > 37000000 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Number of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation events that follow First Look-Please submit updates within the same case
Metric: Number of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities for cases where activity 'First Look-Please submit updates' occurs

Name: Percentage of cases containing First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation that also contain Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Co-Author Account Created During Manuscript Submission'

Name: Frequency of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation relative to the total number of \First Look\ related activities
Metric: Number of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities

Name: Percentage of variants in which First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation occurs exactly once
Metric: the average of the function base == 1 where base is the number of times `ACTIVITY` == 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation'

Name: Number of times First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation is followed by Manuscript Export Succeeded within 24 hours
Metric: Number of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' activities for cases where activity 'Manuscript Export Succeeded' occurs

Name: Ratio of First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation occurrences to the total number of submission confirmation-type activities (including Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation, Revised Manuscript Submission Confirmation, and Resubmission Manuscript Submission Confirmation)
Metric: Percentage of 'First Look Manuscript Submission Confirmation' out of all 'Original Manuscript Submission Confirmation'
